<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Reckless" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Reckless</orth> (O. Edd. <emph>reckless</emph> or <emph>wreakless</emph>), careless, thoughtless: <cit><quote>the love of r. Silvia,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 5.2.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. V, 2, 52</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>careless, r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 4.2.150" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 2, 150</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>so flies the r. shepherd from the wolf,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.6.7" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 6, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you grave but r. senators,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 3.1.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 1, 92</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I am r. what I do,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 3.1.110" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 1, 110</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a puffed and r. libertine,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.3.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 3, 49</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>